FBIS3-28119 "dreas023_a_94027" FBIS-EAS-94-023 Document Type:Daily Report 3 February 1994 NORTHEAST ASIA Japan Controversy Over Tax Reform Proposal Reported Stimulus Package Meeting Postponed OW0302114294 Tokyo KYODO in English 1135 GMT 3 Feb 94 OW0302114294 Tokyo KYODO Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Tokyo, Feb. 3 KYODO -- The Economic Planning Agency said Thursday [3 February] it decided not to hold an economic ministers' meeting to decide on the government's fresh pump-priming package during the day. The adoption of the stimulative package, originally scheduled for Thursday, will be put off until Friday or afterward, agency officials said.
